node.title: Human remains found on beach in North Canterbury
node.description: Human remains have washed ashore at Leithfield Beach in Hurunui, police have been told.
node.content:
["Human remains have washed ashore at Leithfield Beach in Hurunui, police have been told.", "", "
\nPhoto: Find a Beach\n
", "Police received the information from a member of the public around 8.30am today.", "At this time, the remains are unidentified and the circumstances are unknown, police said in a statement.", "Anyone with information or concerns that can assist in an inquiry is asked to contact police on 105 and quote event number P049212549."]
